      <title>美国最高法院驳回针对 Nvidia 的证券欺诈诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-supreme-court-tosses-case-involving-securities-fraud-suit-against-nvidia-2024-12-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院周三回避了关于是否允许股东继续提起证券欺诈诉讼的决定，该诉讼指控人工智能芯片制造商英伟达误导投资者，称其销售额在多大程度上依赖于动荡的加密货币市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-supreme-court-tosses-case-involving-securities-fraud-suit-against-nvidia-2024-12-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 15:08:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
