      <title>希腊计划降低零售客户的银行费用</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/greece-plans-lower-bank-fees-retail-customers-2024-12-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊财政部长周三表示，希腊政府正在制定计划降低银行零售交易费用，以帮助家庭应对高昂的生活成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/greece-plans-lower-bank-fees-retail-customers-2024-12-11/</guid>
