      <title>富国银行首席执行官对监管修复表示更有信心</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/wells-fargo-ceo-expresses-more-confidence-regulatory-fixes-2024-12-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富国银行首席执行官查理·沙夫 (Charlie Scharf) 周三表示，对该行在长达多年的虚假账户丑闻之后解决合规问题的进展更加有信心，并详细介绍了该行实施风险控制的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/wells-fargo-ceo-expresses-more-confidence-regulatory-fixes-2024-12-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 14:33:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>焦点：消息人士称，在 Banco BPM 强行收购之前，UniCredit 的 Orcel 正在策划收购</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/unicredits-orcel-was-plotting-bid-before-banco-bpm-forced-hand-sources-say-2024-12-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两位知情人士称，裕信银行首席执行官安德里亚·奥塞尔 (Andrea Orcel) 多年来一直在制定接管 BPM 银行的计划，并且几乎已经做好了采取行动的准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/unicredits-orcel-was-plotting-bid-before-banco-bpm-forced-hand-sources-say-2024-12-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 14:22:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
