      <title>2024 年收购狂潮过后，贝莱德进军私募市场的步伐可能仍未结束</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/blackrocks-private-markets-push-may-not-be-over-after-2024-buyout-spree-2024-12-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德在 2024 年可能会继续大举交易，因为这家全球最大的资产管理公司预计将抓住机会进一步拓展私人信贷、房地产、基础设施或私募股权领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/blackrocks-private-markets-push-may-not-be-over-after-2024-buyout-spree-2024-12-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 11:13:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
